\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi-567 (b)\u8195?\~Write an SQL query that will update the QuantityInStock of the product with ProductID 1 when this sale is made. The value 3 should be subtracted from the current quantity in stock.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi0 ___________________________________________________________________\par
