\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi-567 (c)\u8195?\~Complete the following SQL statement to create the Animal relation, including the key field.\par
\f2\fs20\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb0\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi0 CREATE TABLE Animal (\f1\fs22\sb240 ______________________________________________\par
