\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567 ___________________________________________________________________\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567 __________________________________________________________________\f2\fs20 )\par
\f1\fs20\cf0\b\ltrpar\qr\sb60\sa0\li0\ri0 (3)\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi-567 (d)\u8195?\~\b Figure 1\b0  is repeated below to help you answer part (d).\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\b\ltrpar\qc\sb240\sa0\li0\ri0\fi0 Figure 1 (repeated)\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1701\ri567 Zoo(\ul ZooName\ul0 , Town, Country)\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb90\sa0\li1701\ri567 AnimalLocation(\ul AnimalID\ul0 , \ul ZooName\ul0 , \ul DateArrived\ul0 , DateLeft)\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb90\sa0\li1701\ri567 Animal(\ul AnimalID\ul0 , IndividualName, Species, DateOfBirth, Sex)\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb90\sa0\li1701\ri567 Match(\ul AnimalFemaleID\ul0 , \ul AnimalMaleID\ul0 , \ul DateOfMatch\ul0 , Successful)\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567 There is a requirement to identify all of the red pandas that were present at the zoo called \u8216?Ashdale Park\u8217? at any time between 01/04/2020 and 31/05/2020, inclusive.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567 The animals might still be at the zoo or may have moved to another zoo.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567 Write a query that will list all the red pandas that were at the zoo on any day between these dates.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567 For each red panda on the list, the animal\u8217?s individual name and the date that the animal arrived at the zoo, and no other fields, should be listed.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567 ___________________________________________________________________\par
