\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi-567 (e)\u8195?\~It is proposed that an additional attribute, ZooName, is added to the Animal relation. This will store the name of the zoo that currently has the animal. No other changes would be made to the database.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi0 Describe \b one advantage\b0  and \b one disadvantage\b0  of adding this new attribute to the relation.\par
