\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi-567 (b)\u8195?\~A different design was originally proposed for the database. This design did not have the Customer relation and had the following design for the Booking relation:\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1701\ri567\fi0 Booking(\ul FacilityID\ul0 , \ul BookingDate\ul0 , \ul StartTime\ul0 , EndTime, Forename, Surname, EmailAddress)\par
