\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi-567 (d)\u8195?\~A composite primary key has been selected for the Viewing relation. This consists of the attributes BuyerID, PropertyID and ViewingDate.\par
