\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li567\ri567 Figure 1\b0  is repeated below so that you can answer part (e) without having to turn back in the question paper.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\b\ltrpar\qc\sb240\sa0\li0\ri0 Figure 1\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1701\ri567\fi-567 Property(\ul PropertyID\ul0 , HouseNum, Street, Area, Postcode, Bedrooms, Bathrooms, AskingPrice, SellerID)\par
