\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi-567 (c)\u8195?\~The SQL query in \b Figure 2\b0  has been written to produce a list of all of the vets who work at the surgery in the town of Torquay. Some errors have been made in the query.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\b\ltrpar\qc\sb240\sa0\li0\ri0\fi0 Figure 2\par
