\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi-567 (d)\u8195?\~The database is stored at the practice\u8217?s head office. Staff at the individual surgeries access it using a client-server database system, which enables the management of concurrent access to the database.\par
