\f1\fs27\cf1\ltrpar\ql\sb450\sa45\li150\ri45 Q11.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb0\sa0\li567\ri567 Two methods that can be used to manage concurrent access are:\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi-567 \u8226?\u8195?\u8195?\~record locks\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb0\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi-567 \u8226?\u8195?\u8195?\~timestamp ordering.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li567\ri567\fi0 Select \b one\b0  of these methods and describe how it manages concurrent access.\par
