\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567 A list is to be produced of the names of all athletes who are competing in the fixture that is taking place on 17/09/18. The list must include the Surname, Forename and DateOfBirth of these athletes and no other details. The list should be presented in alphabetical order by Surname.\par
