\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li567\ri567 This list must include the PartID, Description, Price (each) and QuantityUsed of each part, and no other details. The parts in the list should be ordered by PartID with the parts with the lowest PartIDs nearest to the top of the list.\par
